replies.body:
Body language is a great way, as well as VO (which Riot are amazing at tbh). I do agree that the over exaggerated face works well when it comes to communicating emotion, especially with energetic personas such as Zoe. And yeah... Annie isn't the most appealing champ at first glance..
Anyways, I'm sure it's a very abstract line when it comes to making an expressive character and trying to stay within the aesthetic of the game
